
|--------------------------------------------------------------------------
| Resistance Gene Identifier - RGI 
|--------------------------------------------------------------------------


|--------------------------------------------------------------------------
| Install the tarball using pip - Mac or linux
|--------------------------------------------------------------------------

	1. sudo pip install RGI-X.tar.gz

|--------------------------------------------------------------------------
| Running RGI
|--------------------------------------------------------------------------

	1. Installed programs Help menu:	

		$ sudo rgi -h

		$ sudo rgi_clean -h

		$ sudo rgi_jsontab -h

		$ sudo rgi_jsonformat -h

		$ sudo rgi_load -h


|--------------------------------------------------------------------------
| Uninstall RGI using pip - Mac or linux
|--------------------------------------------------------------------------

	1. sudo pip uninstall rgi

